OL,3,CLiam Payne: Hotel guest describes
OL,4,Cseeing him minutes before his death
OL,6,FHotel guest Bret Watson told ITV News'
OL,7,FDan Rivers that he had "multiple
OL,8,Fencounters" with Liam Payne on the day
OL,9,Fof his death
OL,11,FWarning: Readers may find some details
OL,12,Fin this article distressing
OL,14,FA hotel guest has described witnessing
OL,15,FLiam Payne in the hours and minutes
OL,16,Fbefore his fatal fall from a third-
OL,17,Ffloor balcony at a hotel in Buenos
OL,18,FAires on Wednesday, in an exclusive
OL,19,Finterview with ITV News.
