OL,3,CLiam Payne: Hotel guest describes
OL,4,Cseeing him minutes before his death
OL,6,FBret Watson, from Chicago, was staying
OL,7,Fat the Casa Sur Palermo Hotel in the
OL,8,FArgentinian capital ahead of his
OL,9,Fwedding, when he said he had "multiple
OL,10,Fencounters" with the One Direction
OL,11,Fstar, who was staying in the same
OL,12,Fhotel.
OL,14,FThe 34-year-old explained how he and
OL,15,Fhis other wedding guests saw Payne
OL,16,F"causing a disturbance" minutes before
OL,17,Fhis death.
