OL,3,CLiam Payne: Hotel guest describes
OL,4,Cseeing him minutes before his death
OL,6,FAt one point Payne appeared to have
OL,7,F"actually passed out" in the lobby
OL,8,Fbefore he "had to be physically taken
OL,9,Fback up to his room," Watson said.
OL,11,FHe said: "So we're here with a couple
OL,12,Fof other guests in the hotel and we
OL,13,Fwere in the lobby just waiting for
OL,14,Fsome people to arrive and that's when
OL,15,Fwe had multiple encounters with Liam.
OL,17,F"Multiple times (Liam) had come down
OL,18,Fto the lobby, was causing a
OL,19,Fdisturbance, kept being escorted back
OL,20,Fup to his room.
