OL,3,CLiam Payne: Hotel guest describes
OL,4,Cseeing him minutes before his death
OL,6,F"There was an incident where he was
OL,7,Fvery frustrated and was smashing his
OL,8,Flaptop in the lobby. And then the
OL,9,Ffinal time he came back down, he
OL,10,Factually passed out in the lobby of
OL,11,Fthe hotel, started, looked like (he
OL,12,Fwas) convulsing a little bit and had
OL,13,Fto be physically taken back up to his
OL,14,Froom.
OL,16,F"And that was about five minutes
OL,17,Fbefore the eventual incident that
OL,18,Fhappened."
