OL,3,CLiam Payne: Hotel guest describes
OL,4,Cseeing him minutes before his death
OL,6,FWatson had taken a picture of Payne in
OL,7,Fthe lobby of the hotel earlier in the
OL,8,Fday. In it, he is lying on a sofa
OL,9,Flooking at emails on his laptop.
OL,11,FWatson also recalled the moment later
OL,12,Fthat day when he saw the pop star fall
OL,13,Fto his death.
OL,15,F"I was in my hotel room, two floors
OL,16,Fbelow and directly below and saw the
OL,17,Fbody fall through, looking out the
OL,18,Fwindow, saw the body fall and
OL,19,Fobviously heard the aftermath and
OL,20,Fcould see his body on the ground
OL,21,Fafterwards."
