OL,3,CLiam Payne: Hotel guest describes
OL,4,Cseeing him minutes before his death
OL,6,FHotel staff had called police amidst
OL,7,Fthe incident, warning of an
OL,8,F"aggressive man who could be under the
OL,9,Finfluence of drugs or alcohol".
OL,11,FIn a 911 call released on Thursday,
OL,12,Fthe hotel manager can be heard saying
OL,13,Fthey have a guest "drunk with drugs
OL,14,Fand alcohol.
OL,16,F"We need to send someone with urgency
OL,17,Fbecause I don't know if the guest's
OL,18,Flife is in danger because he is in a
OL,19,Froom with balcony, and we are afraid
OL,20,Fhe could do something that threatens
OL,21,Flife," the hotel manager added.
