OL,3,CLiam Payne: Hotel guest describes
OL,4,Cseeing him minutes before his death
OL,6,FSoon after police arrived, they were
OL,7,Ftold a loud sound had been heard in
OL,8,Fthe hotel's interior courtyard, where
OL,9,Fthey later discovered Payne's body.
OL,11,FMedics confirmed his death at the
OL,12,Fscene. He was 31 years old.
OL,14,FBuenos Aires police said the singer's
OL,15,Ffall resulted in "extremely serious
OL,16,Finjuries."
