OL,3,CLiam Payne: Hotel guest describes
OL,4,Cseeing him minutes before his death
OL,6,FThe prosecutor's office indicated the
OL,7,Fmusician was alone when the fall
OL,8,Foccurred and said he appeared to be
OL,9,F"going through some kind of outbreak
OL,10,Fdue to substance abuse".
OL,12,FTributes have poured in from fans and
OL,13,Fcelebrities around the world after the
OL,14,Fnews of the star's death became public.
OL,16,FA statement signed by his former One
OL,17,FDirection band mates, Harry Styles,
OL,18,FZayn Malik, Louis Tomlinson and Niall
OL,19,FHoran on Thursday night said: "We're
OL,20,Fcompletely devastated by the news of
OL,21,FLiam's passing.
