OL,3,CLiam Payne: Hotel guest describes
OL,4,Cseeing him minutes before his death
OL,6,F"In time, and when everyone is able
OL,7,Fto, there will be more to say. But for
OL,8,Fnow, we will take some time to grieve
OL,9,Fand process the loss of our brother,
OL,10,Fwho we loved dearly.
OL,12,F"The memories we shared with him will
OL,13,Fbe treasured forever. For now, our
OL,14,Fthoughts are with his family, his
OL,15,Ffriends, and the fans who loved him
OL,16,Falongside us.
OL,18,F"We will miss him terribly. We love
OL,19,Fyou Liam."
